&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Identify, pitch, and close new opportunities within a large enterprise account.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Personally and consistently build and deepen rapport, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;deliver samples, and host onsite meetings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; with client stakeholders — &lt;strong&gt;face-to-face relationship building is key.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Leverage &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Salesforce&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; to manage your time strategically —&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;time-blocking&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; to ensure urgent administrative tasks are handled without losing focus on activities that drive the business forward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Most companies claim to have the best people. We say to them, &quot;Keep dreaming.&quot; Our people are second to none. They set us apart with their entrepreneurial spirit and ambition. They come to us from the likes of Amazon, Microsoft, Nordstrom, Starbucks and the sports world, bringing energy, bold ideas and a willingness to dive into the unfamiliar. It&#39;s our people that make BDA the top global Merchandise Agency to work for.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POSITION SUMMARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
