&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11.0pt;&quot;&gt;To be considered, you must &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;live within commuting distance&lt;/span&gt;, as regular in-person collaboration is a key part of the role.&lt;/p&gt;
