&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Possible Project Work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Depending on the project, freelance support may include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trend Research &amp;amp; Inspiration Boards&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Researching and compiling trend boards that highlight emerging design, merchandise, collectible, and consumer trends relevant to the client, audience, and industry.&lt;/p&gt;
